{"tid":1777852,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭為失業建制區議員派公職 真係將呢個制度最黑暗面擺上台面","createTime":"2019-12-10T13:38:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T13:56:15.000Z","uid":61690,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7acc5489d85415dae5859692c3da487ac2b18536","tid":1777852,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:38:08.000Z","msg":"傳送門:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191210/60361494?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2G_VJfKynS1-DSPvklQRIab5FlHH6oKtSbPO-fcUdAu2fEzG_31eedUKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191210%2F60361494%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2G_VJfKynS1-DSPvklQRIab5FlHH6oKtSbPO-fcUdAu2fEzG_31eedUKs&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3catywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=b4bdd4fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191210%2F60361494%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2G_VJfKynS1-DSPvklQRIab5FlHH6oKtSbPO-fcUdAu2fEzG_31eedUKs&h=72c20dee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191210/60361494?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2G_VJfKynS1-DSPvklQRIab5FlHH6oKtSbPO-fcUdAu2fEzG_31eedUKs</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個政府真係好醜陋，輸打嬴要。相反，建制嬴區選果陣又唔見佢派公職俾泛民？唔make sense wor 老細，你係唔係傻撚左？定當香港人個個都係毅進仔？<br />\n<br />\n政府公帑來自市民，當大部份市民都唔鋸建制既時候，但政府竟然夠膽擅自拎公帑黎俾著數自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所謂現存既定既制度都幾兒戲。說穿了，就係政府想點就點，you have no stake in the society．<br />\n<br />\n結論，要解決問題，首先要解決呢個制度，我要雙普選。完。"},{"pid":"a24ad843ee4501a79d92ca